The Petri Graph Neural Network (PGNN) offers an extended form of traditional GNN frameworks, by incorporating the notion of multimodal message passing, afforded by heterogeneous network flow23. The PGNN forward pass consists of an MMP multimodal message passing phase, in line with Eq. (9), followed by MMP message aggregation10\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
